    "en": {
      "title": "A Kurunegala school student gets stuck in a city drain",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police say that the police and the army together rescued a student from the school in Kurunegala area after half an hour and took him to the hospital.",
        "The incident came to light when a bag was found near the drain and the child was taken out by digging the drain with a backhoe.",
        "With the heavy rain that fell in Kurunegala and other areas since this morning, the roads and canals in that area are full of water and it is known that this child slipped and fell into the drain.",
        "The child is currently being treated in the intensive care unit of the Kurunegala hospital."
      ],
